column5: Jigman, I sent you an e-mail yesterday from your profile page. Just wondering if you received it? I had some questions about MLO. If you did get it and can respond, please respond to my home email on the profile page and the my work email. Thank you Roddy
Sorry, haven't checked my home email. Will try to do so tonight. Did send an email to your profile add. Will send another once I get your message.
Jigman, I sent you another e-mail last night. I had problems with your reply. Roddy
I promise to get back to you this weekend. Sorry again.
Hey, let me know if my email got to you or not. Always happy to talk MLO
